thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Mumster

author: Mumster
title: Mumster
text: Rapid pickup from the Christchurch airport with a relaxed sorting of the paperwork. Child seats free and fitted. 7 year old car, seen a few miles and cosmetic scrapes, but was a very good motor. Couldn't fault it for the price, and you don't standout as a tourist. Bit of an effort to return the car out of hours at Wellington, but it got sorted in a fairly relaxed way (the reason I didn't give 5 star). Have used before, will use again, recommend to anyone (unless you like shiny motors).
